OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FThe Labour Party appears to be heading
OL,7,Ftowards a leadership contest where
OL,8,Fseveral senior figures plan to
OL,9,Fchallenge Sir Keir Starmer and oust
OL,10,Fhim as Prime Minister.
OL,12,FWes Streeting, the former health
OL,13,Fsecretary, has said he will stand in
OL,14,Fany contest while Greater Manchester
OL,15,FMayor Andy Burnham is hoping to return
OL,16,Fto Westminster in an upcoming by-
OL,17,Felection to allow him a chance to tilt
OL,18,Ffor the top job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
