OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FHere the Press Association looks at
OL,7,Fthe possible candidates should a
OL,8,FLabour leadership contest be triggered.
OL,10,F` Wes Streeting
OL,12,FFormer health secretary Mr Streeting
OL,13,Fquit Government last week and hit out
OL,14,Fat the incremental approach of Sir
OL,15,FKeir's administration in his
OL,16,Fresignation letter to the Prime
OL,17,FMinister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
