CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778976177
OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FOn Saturday, Mr Streeting set out his
OL,7,Ffledgling policy platform, which
OL,8,Fincluded a call for a "new special
OL,9,Frelationship" with the EU, which he
OL,10,Fsaid could eventually lead to Britain
OL,11,Frejoining the trade bloc.
OL,13,FMr Streeting also called for the UK to
OL,14,Freindustrialise in order to grow the
OL,15,Feconomy and fund social democratic
OL,16,Fpolicies.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
