CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778976177
OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FThe ex-minister suggested he wanted to
OL,7,Fsee the UK meet the challenge of
OL,8,Fdisinformation on social media with
OL,9,Fthe 21st century's equivalent of the
OL,10,FBBC but was vague about what this
OL,11,Fmight practically entail.
OL,13,F` Andy Burnham
OL,15,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor has made
OL,16,Fit clear he wishes to be Labour's
OL,17,Fcandidate for the upcoming Makerfield
OL,18,Fby-election, which will be held after
OL,19,Fthe local Labour MP, Josh Simons,
OL,20,Fresigned to allow Mr Burnham a chance
OL,21,Fto return to Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
