OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FMr Burnham has sought to promote his
OL,7,F"Manchesterism" brand of politics as
OL,8,Fan antidote to the Westminster system
OL,9,Fof Government in recent months.
OL,11,FHe has claimed Westminster no longer
OL,12,Fworks for the majority of the country,
OL,13,Fpromoting ideas including a move
OL,14,Ftowards a more proportional system of
OL,15,Fvoting, taxes on wealth and replacing
OL,16,Fthe House of Lords as a means of
OL,17,Fmaking the system fairer.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
