OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778976177
OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FIn interviews over the weekend, Mr
OL,7,FBurnham also indicated he wanted to
OL,8,Fsee Britain reindustrialise to provide
OL,9,Fgood jobs more widely.
OL,11,FHe has also previously indicated
OL,12,Fsupport for rejoining the EU.
OL,14,F` Angela Rayner
OL,16,FThe former deputy prime minister left
OL,17,FGovernment over a scandal about her
OL,18,Ftax affairs but this has been resolved
OL,19,Fwithout any penalty from HMRC,
OL,20,Fclearing Ms Rayner for a potential
OL,21,Fleadership bid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
