OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FMs Rayner has not yet made any public
OL,7,Fdeclaration that she would stand in
OL,8,Fany Labour leadership contest but her
OL,9,Fannouncement that she had been cleared
OL,10,Fby HMRC appeared to be timed to
OL,11,Fcoincide with other rivals setting out
OL,12,Ftheir stall to replace Sir Keir.
OL,14,FWhile serving in Government as deputy
OL,15,Fprime minister, Labour's then deputy
OL,16,Fleader and housing secretary
OL,17,Fchampioned a series of reforms to
OL,18,Fworkers' rights, which have largely
OL,19,Fbeen carried through after her exit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
