OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FIn a signal of what her policy
OL,7,Fplatform may look like, Ms Rayner has
OL,8,Fhit out at several decisions by
OL,9,Fcolleagues since returning to the
OL,10,Fbackbenches.
OL,12,FFor example, she described plans by
OL,13,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood to
OL,14,Ftighten up the eligibility for
OL,15,Fmigrants who have lived in the UK for
OL,16,Fyears to claim permanent settlement as
OL,17,F"un-British".
OL,19,F` Ed Miliband
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
