OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,FSeveral reports in the media have
OL,7,Fsuggested the Energy Secretary would
OL,8,Fbe interested in standing should a
OL,9,Fcontest for the Labour leadership be
OL,10,Fheld.
OL,12,FHowever sources close to Mr Miliband
OL,13,Fdismissed in the week rumours he was
OL,14,Fpreparing a bid as "mischief-making".
OL,16,FMr Miliband, who led the Labour Party
OL,17,Fin opposition between 2010 and 2015,
OL,18,Fhas largely stuck to speaking about
OL,19,Fhis brief as Energy Secretary since
OL,20,Fthe party came to power in 2024.
OL,26,@vD@TOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
