OL,3,CWho are the senior Labour figures
OL,4,Cvying to replace Sir Keir Starmer?
OL,6,F` Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,FThe Prime Minister has insisted he
OL,9,Fwill not be forced out of office by
OL,10,Fhis "doubters" and has insisted he
OL,11,Fwill prove them wrong.
OL,13,FIn a speech reacting to the bruising
OL,14,Fdefeat Labour suffered in elections
OL,15,Facross England, Wales and Scotland
OL,16,Flast week, Sir Keir set out a series
OL,17,Fof measures aimed at moving the dial
OL,18,Ffor his Government.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
